node.text:
Available on February 1st exclusively at BAPE STORE® MIAMI and release on us.bape.com on February 8th. The first 100 customers who purchase a collaboration item at the Miami store will be eligible to attend the J Balvin meet and greet.
This will be a first come, first serve release. Store lineup will begin at 8 am EST and the store will be open at 9 am EST. Any customer that lineup before 8 am and/or do any overnight camping at the store will not be eligible to purchase ANY ITEM and will be asked to leave the vicinity. 
Customers who are eligible to meet J Balvin will receive a wristband that must be worn after receiving the wristband and will be asked to come back at a later time for the meet and greet. Customers with broken wristbands in any way will not be allowed to participate. 
@jbalvin  @miamidesigndistrict  @karizmavisuals  #bape #jbalvin
#miamidesigndistrict

node.text:
The BAPEX® timepiece range from A BATHING APE® has produced several classic and collectable accessories over the last few years. It is therefore no surprise that when new designs get released, they create a buzz in the fashion community and the new items are immediately in high demand.

Available Saturday, July 17th at BAPE STORE® locations and on US.BAPE.COM. 

#bape #abathingape #bapex

The BE@RBRICK Karimoku BABY MILO® is a 400% wooden BE@RBRICK (approx. 280mm in length), handcrafted by skilled furniture craftsmen, with the Karimoku logo engraved on the inside of the left foot. 
This will go on sale on Saturday, July 17th, in limited quantities at US.BAPE.COM, BAPE STORE®️ locations, and Medicom Toy stores.

#bape #abathingape #babymilo 
#medicomtoy #bearbrick #karimoku

node.text:
BMX FLATLAND RIDERS SHOW OFF FRESH BAPE STA™ DESIGNS
Rocking the latest BAPE®️ gear, a group of bikers hit the streets to freestyle flatland tricks in the new BAPE®️ SK8 STA and BAPE STA 93 HI collections. Serving stylish combinations of tailwhips and spins, the bikers stunning technique is matched only by the unique variety of footwear on display. The new BAPE STA™ collections will be available at BAPE STORE®️ locations and online on Saturday, July 17th. 

#bape #abathingape #bapesta #bapesta93hi #bapesk8sta

 SUMMER BAG will be available at BAPE STORE® locations on Saturday, July 10th.
